  "body": "This started with this PR https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/4505\r\n\r\nThe problem that it solved was that switching channels was slow, because sometimes, it would load most if not all messages in the UI, even if they were not visible.\r\n\r\nThe solution in that PR is pretty hack-ish. It works well, but it could cause issues in the long run with memory usage.\r\n\r\nSo we need to investigate the initial issue of why the channel loading loads all these messages for no reason.\r\n\r\nOnce that is fixed, we can update the ChatColumnView to update the Loaders like explained here: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/4963#pullrequestreview-899945161",
